citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:05 am to
11:35 pm on 09-Jan-18.
Attempts to make contact with the licensee were done by knocking on the door, honking the GOV's horn, waiting in
the driveway for 30 minutes and calling the licensee's phone number but was unable to leave a message.
